James O. NEWHOUSE, Petitioner, v. DEPARTMENT OF THE AIR FORCE, Respondent. No. 05-3024. United States Court of Appeals, Federal Circuit. Aug. 17, 2005.

Before NEWMAN, Circuit Judge, ARCHER, Senior Circuit Judge, and SCHALL, Circuit Judge.

JUDGMENT

PER CURIAM.

This CAUSE having been heard and considered, it is ORDERED and ADJUDGED: AFFIRMED. See Fed. Cir. R. 36
